WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.688 --> 00:00:13.920
See if they can see us.

00:00:16.547 --> 00:00:26.595
Comment if you can hear us.

00:00:29.169 --> 00:00:30.719
Hello, everybody.

00:00:30.719 --> 00:00:32.079
Good morning, family.

00:00:32.079 --> 00:00:36.840
I'm not used to doing live video, so it's very strange for me.

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:56.974
I appreciate you all joining me tonight.

00:00:56.974 --> 00:01:21.743
My heart is heavy for the people in New Orleans.

00:01:21.743 --> 00:02:31.025
When the Lord showed me that on October 27th, He showed me a man going down Bourbon Street and doing what he did, and it's very sad.

00:02:31.025 --> 00:02:58.138
People say, 'Brandon, you got it right; you saw that.

00:02:58.138 --> 00:03:47.560
' Then they say, 'Well, you didn't get Tennessee right, but you saw Las Vegas and that happened.

00:03:47.560 --> 00:04:30.992
' Folks, I'm looking over in the spirit, and the Lord is showing me what I'm seeing.

00:04:30.992 --> 00:04:55.960
I'm praying for these things not to happen.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:05:22.447
That's the bottom line: we don't want this stuff to happen.

00:05:22.447 --> 00:05:50.160
We don't want to see this in the news.

00:06:06.053 --> 00:06:24.500
To me, that is a prayer failure whenever you see something tragic taking place.

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:54.920
When the Lord is warning you about something, it's to stop it.

00:07:02.660 --> 00:07:16.625
You might say, 'Well, you missed it prophetically.

00:07:16.625 --> 00:07:31.919
' I don't consider myself a prophet.

00:07:40.249 --> 00:08:07.659
I say it a thousand times; I believe I'm a Watchman.

00:08:07.659 --> 00:08:52.951
The Lord has called Diana and me to raise up a million-person prayer army, and that's what we're doing.

00:08:52.951 --> 00:09:44.519
We're so excited about Asia and what's happening with our Asia channels; the gospel is being spread throughout the whole world.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:10:43.905
But whenever you see a tragic event like the one in New Orleans over the last 24 hours, I feel we failed.

00:10:55.550 --> 00:11:34.200
I grieve because those people were down there partying and drinking, and we don't know where their souls were with the Lord.

00:11:39.509 --> 00:12:22.360
We pray they knew Jesus Christ and had a saving knowledge of Him because it's a very hard time for their families.

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:47.390
It's a terrible way to start out this beautiful 2025.

00:12:47.390 --> 00:13:11.208
I pray for them and weep with their families.

00:13:17.244 --> 00:13:35.747
The Lord showed me a major event taking place in Nevada.

00:13:38.148 --> 00:14:25.968
He showed me those three men and told me that there are major cells throughout America and that they had plans.

00:14:33.851 --> 00:14:46.645
The Lord even brought up the name ISIS.

00:14:46.645 --> 00:15:04.131
He showed me Bourbon Street and these things.

00:15:04.131 --> 00:15:46.343
Pray for Nashville and for families to always be in the right place at the right time.

00:15:46.343 --> 00:16:56.693
It is so important in these last days for you to be filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, listening to Him on everything you do.

00:17:06.900 --> 00:17:15.580
The days are going to get very dark.

00:17:15.785 --> 00:18:02.900
I told you 2025 for the remnant—there are two prophetic words that the Lord showed me.

00:18:03.799 --> 00:18:32.240
For the bride, for the remnant, it was like the ten virgins.

00:18:32.240 --> 00:19:57.880
Five had their lamps full of oil and were expecting the bridegroom, and the ones that did not have their lamps full of oil had to rush off and try to find oil because the bridegroom was coming.

00:20:00.319 --> 00:20:56.280
I want to be the one that has my lamp full of oil in these last days because of how serious the hour is.

00:20:56.280 --> 00:21:57.095
We are going to see very dark days, folks, but we are the ones that are going to be the light in the darkness.

00:21:57.095 --> 00:22:17.406
People will come like bugs to a light.

00:22:22.080 --> 00:23:20.351
The Lord showed me even in this last vision on December 26th—on Diana's birthday when we had the visitation—He showed me people had catchers' mitts in their hands.

00:23:20.351 --> 00:24:10.069
Like in baseball, we would be the ones with the catchers' mitts ready to catch the lost in 2025.

00:24:10.069 --> 00:24:45.765
People are looking for authenticity in these last days, not religious, fake stuff.

00:24:45.765 --> 00:25:33.947
Many preachers are preaching AI sermons that don't come from the Spirit of God; it's coming from a computer.

00:25:37.840 --> 00:26:30.577
People are wanting a true and authentic move of God, and I believe God has raised up Diana and me to talk about the real.

00:26:30.577 --> 00:26:45.791
I don't like fake religious stuff.

00:26:45.791 --> 00:27:06.080
It's not about Brandon getting it right.

00:27:06.080 --> 00:27:43.399
I want Jesus to say, 'Well done, thou good and faithful servant.

00:27:43.399 --> 00:28:21.076
' It's about deflecting the glory of man and putting it on the Father.

00:28:21.076 --> 00:29:19.729
No matter how many times you get it right or how many times people call you a false prophet, it's all about Jesus.

00:29:36.754 --> 00:30:12.480
I remember I was driving down I-35 by Edmond, and I was exiting off of Covell Street.

00:30:17.159 --> 00:30:59.399
The Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, very sobering days are coming in the near future.

00:30:59.399 --> 00:31:38.479
' He said to be filled with and controlled by My Spirit to bubbling over.

00:31:38.479 --> 00:32:03.897
That's how you're going to maintain a backbone like a crowbar.

00:32:03.897 --> 00:32:32.310
Treat your Bible like we do our cell phones.

00:32:32.310 --> 00:32:37.919
Smith Wigglesworth would get out his Bible every 15 minutes and feed on the word of God.

00:32:37.919 --> 00:33:10.783
That's what gives you power and changes you from glory to glory.

00:33:29.519 --> 00:34:16.230
It's not some YouTuber or some prophetic word that's going to set you free; it's having a relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:34:16.230 --> 00:35:03.240
The more you get in that word, the more it's going to change you from the inside out.

00:35:11.389 --> 00:35:50.183
In these last days, the Bible says we will know His voice, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:35:54.844 --> 00:36:21.116
You have that inward, still, small voice on the inside of you.

00:36:21.116 --> 00:37:22.413
Father, I thank You that You're speaking to me and showing me the plans You have for me and Diana.

00:37:22.413 --> 00:37:41.407
He knows your future, ladies and gentlemen.

00:37:41.407 --> 00:38:03.484
He wants you to have life more abundantly.

00:38:16.249 --> 00:38:25.433
The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:38:25.433 --> 00:39:07.170
That's what happened in New Orleans and Las Vegas—places that have an open door through sin.

00:39:07.170 --> 00:40:38.866
But if you have the blood of Jesus and you're holding that blood against him, the name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run into it and are safe.

00:40:38.866 --> 00:41:31.049
As long as you keep Jesus number one and keep those doors shut, I believe in divine protection.

00:41:31.049 --> 00:42:36.390
The Lord told me that for the days that are coming, we will have to have a deep knowledge of Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

00:42:36.390 --> 00:42:59.938
I told you I saw a plague coming—COVID on steroids.

00:42:59.938 --> 00:43:36.394
But we know the honey glow is all about Jesus and what He's going to do.

00:43:36.394 --> 00:43:59.186
He's going to anoint you to withstand the enemy's attack.

00:43:59.186 --> 00:44:16.270
No weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:44:22.261 --> 00:45:04.789
The Lord showed me major attacks trying to come against mega-churches in Houston, Tampa, and North Carolina.

00:45:10.417 --> 00:45:51.840
I saw a lot of people coming in with a lot of mass shootings trying to hurt folks.

00:45:59.660 --> 00:46:26.119
It's smart to have police officers and security at your church to protect your congregation.

00:46:29.832 --> 00:47:34.060
I saw cells of people coming not only from the southern border but from the northern border in Toronto.

00:47:34.060 --> 00:48:07.154
Interceding for a peaceful transition of power and praying for Trump's protection.

00:48:08.040 --> 00:48:32.325
The enemy will try to touch what he loves.

00:48:33.110 --> 00:49:13.815
I saw the Lord cracking His whip like a lion tamer towards the dragons and the bear.

00:49:16.708 --> 00:49:35.249
It made them pause, but it did not destroy them.

00:49:35.249 --> 00:49:55.760
We must intercede for him to finish his race.

00:49:55.760 --> 00:50:24.186
This channel is bringing a million-person prayer army for the glory of God.

00:50:24.186 --> 00:50:33.400
Prayer changes things.

00:50:33.400 --> 00:51:04.960
You'll know the truth, and the truth will make you free.

00:51:09.725 --> 00:52:06.056
You need a Rhema word that becomes alive inside of you; it's having a Rhema word of God that tells you what it is.

00:52:11.302 --> 00:52:27.594
The Holy Spirit brings it to life.

00:52:27.594 --> 00:53:34.622
It's life to those that find them and health to all their flesh.

00:53:39.320 --> 00:54:02.858
I remember the visitation from the Lord where I saw Him being crucified.

00:54:02.858 --> 00:54:14.955
He said, 'It's the word, Brandon.

00:54:14.955 --> 00:54:37.547
' You have to believe you are saved, healed, and blessed.

00:54:37.547 --> 00:54:40.599
I'm more than a conqueror through Him who loved me.

00:54:40.599 --> 00:54:57.753
Arise and shine, for the light has come.

00:54:57.753 --> 00:55:13.620
Nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:55:16.773 --> 00:56:22.143
I believe there was divine protection in Nevada at Trump's hotel; nobody was standing close to that truck because it was a Cyber Truck and people are drawn to them.

00:56:22.143 --> 00:56:48.325
The guy in the truck died, but nobody else did.

00:56:48.325 --> 00:56:58.455
That's a prayer victory.

00:56:58.455 --> 00:57:36.349
Whatever the devil meant for bad, God is going to turn it for good.

00:57:38.990 --> 00:58:00.000
I command back sevenfold what the devil stole.

00:58:15.855 --> 00:58:22.342
Take authority over your neighborhoods and your churches.

00:58:22.342 --> 00:58:43.759
We make much of the blood of Jesus.

00:58:43.759 --> 00:59:10.142
It's time for us to take our authority in these last days.

00:59:10.142 --> 00:59:39.279
Let's pray for the families and for divine protection over President Trump.

00:59:46.625 --> 00:59:49.131
A great acceleration is coming.

00:59:49.131 --> 01:00:09.559
Father, we plead the blood of Jesus over our families.

01:00:09.559 --> 01:00:31.712
We stand on Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

01:00:32.480 --> 01:00:57.360
2025 will be a year of victory and thriving.

01:00:57.360 --> 01:01:30.485
Father, I pray over the hearts of the people in New Orleans.

01:01:30.485 --> 01:02:03.760
May they find You and know You in this time of pain.

01:02:03.760 --> 01:02:21.760
We always look to Jesus when bad things happen.

01:02:21.760 --> 01:02:49.977
We pray for our law enforcement, the FBI, and the Sheriff's Department.

01:02:49.977 --> 01:03:14.991
Give them supernatural wisdom to expose the darkness.

01:03:14.991 --> 01:03:37.120
There is one last call for a mighty harvest.

01:03:37.120 --> 01:04:00.440
We are the generation that will see the Lord come.

01:04:00.440 --> 01:04:33.495
Jesus is standing there with His hand on the doorknob.

01:04:33.495 --> 01:04:42.035
Is your heart ready?

01:04:42.035 --> 01:04:56.400
None of us are promised tomorrow.

01:04:56.400 --> 01:05:16.400
If you were to die today, where would you spend eternity?

01:05:16.400 --> 01:05:20.138
What did you do with the time He gave you?

01:05:20.138 --> 01:05:47.542
Say this prayer: 'Father, I'm a sinner in need of a savior.

01:05:47.542 --> 01:05:59.911
Forgive me of my sins.

01:05:59.911 --> 01:06:19.340
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:06:20.380 --> 01:06:40.520
I believe You died on the cross and rose again.

01:06:40.520 --> 01:06:45.293
I'm coming home.

01:06:45.293 --> 01:07:22.460
' If you said that, go get baptized and get plugged into a Bible-believing church.

01:07:22.460 --> 01:07:46.097
For whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

01:07:46.097 --> 01:08:06.089
I'm telling you, our redemption is drawing near.

01:08:06.089 --> 01:08:30.525
This video is raw and unedited because that's who we are.

01:08:30.525 --> 01:08:54.690
We pray for South Korea, for those undergoing chemo, and for marriages.

01:08:54.690 --> 01:09:27.936
We believe you are healed from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

01:09:27.936 --> 01:09:40.787
We come against demonic strongholds.

01:09:40.787 --> 01:09:57.693
Suspect in custody, victim unharmed in Vegas—prayer works!

01:09:57.693 --> 01:10:19.725
We come against Alzheimer's and dementia in the name of Jesus.

01:10:19.725 --> 01:10:43.980
Call those things that be not as though they were.

01:10:46.093 --> 01:11:02.137
In 2025, you have the mind of Christ.

01:11:02.137 --> 01:11:33.080
Don't be upset about closed doors; God has something better in store.

01:11:33.080 --> 01:11:43.834
We come against pneumonia.

01:11:43.834 --> 01:11:59.679
We pray for a worldwide revival.

01:11:59.973 --> 01:12:32.960
I listen to the word over and over to overcome learning disabilities.

01:12:32.960 --> 01:12:55.685
I smacked my head on the fireplace earlier—I'm seeing stars!

01:12:55.880 --> 01:13:30.840
I take communion with whatever is available, even a potato chip, for intimacy with the Father.

01:13:30.840 --> 01:14:20.822
I'm focusing on my weight in 2025, getting back on the bike and cutting out Sonic Cokes and Cherry Limeade.

01:14:20.822 --> 01:14:52.711
I'm doing a lot better after getting COVID at the revival in Cassville.

01:14:52.711 --> 01:15:25.454
I remember a man with failing lungs who was healed after I prayed for him.

01:15:25.454 --> 01:15:35.253
It's about faith, not feelings.

01:15:35.253 --> 01:15:46.686
We're going to see deliverances.

01:15:46.686 --> 01:15:58.305
Rebuke demons; don't interview them.

01:15:58.305 --> 01:16:30.457
I've got to go—the Holy Spirit is correcting me for being a bit flaky!

01:16:30.457 --> 01:16:40.199
Jesus loves you.
